# Docker and infra

- Network: `marketplace-network`; named volumes for Postgres, Redis, RabbitMQ data.
- Local full stack: root [docker-compose.yml](docker-compose.yml) (Postgres 5432, Redis 6379, RabbitMQ 5672/15672, Nginx **8080**).
- EC2 web-only: [docker-compose.web.yml](docker-compose.web.yml), `NGINX_PORT=80`.
- Mount [infra/nginx/nginx.conf](infra/nginx/nginx.conf) and `apps/web/public` for static site.
- Healthchecks required for long-running services.
- Do not add Graylog/Ocelot/.NET images to `docker-compose.web.yml` without a dedicated issue.
